      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It is important to talk to your doctor about this new shortness of breath, as it could be a sign that your asthma is worsening or another issue is present. While age can affect lung function, a sudden decrease in your inhaler's effectiveness warrants a professional evaluation. Please do not increase your medication dosage without consulting your healthcare provider.",
      "source": "target",
