    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get what you're saying but i really cant afford to miss more work for urgent care right now. i just need a quick way to manage it till my appointment. what if i take a couple of extra puffs and then maybe some antihistamines too? would that help clear up the breathing or is that a bad combo? i just need to know if it's safe to just push through it for a week or so.",
